Package vialab.mouseToTUIO

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Finger
    This class holds touch event information associated with the same session ID (e.g.all the information associated with someone placing their finger on the screen, dragging it, then removing it.)
    MouseToTUIO
    This class creates a transparent Container that overlays a PApplet and respond to mouse and key events with corresponding TUIO message.
    Simulation
    This class creates TUIO messages depending on mouse events and then sends them out to port 3333.
